law.text:
        The following words as used in this chapter, in addition to their ordinary meaning, shall, unless the context otherwise requires, have the meanings respectively given herein: 
“Beverage”, milk, cream, soda water, mineral or aerated water, ale, beer, ginger ale or similar beverages; 
“Can”, jug, bottle and jar; 
“Vessel”, can, jug, bottle, jar, siphon, fountain and box.
